{"tid":532870,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"讀到好想quit U","createTime":"2018-01-18T08:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T19:33:38.000Z","uid":139921,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c408725b552702268d1509b4022b3e25fab11da3","tid":532870,"uid":139921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:46:54.000Z","msg":"今年year1 所以堂都係自己一個人上 <br />\n見到啲人個個都有自己朋友坐埋一堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我呢個毒撚就自己一個坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係大學一個朋友都無<br />\n好驚到時分組無人肯預我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要semA GPA得2.幾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗到上堂無人肯理我 GPA又爛就好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b974f263028af8c946325674aca14997593b7f","tid":532870,"uid":141837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:47:26.000Z","msg":"add oil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64f079d79d192ee7cc5b1a861438bcea3acc634","tid":532870,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:47:51.000Z","msg":"無玩ocamp？"},{"pid":"35c5f6511977062a677c5f5bcb06564abcab3af8","tid":532870,"uid":23087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"Proactive"},{"pid":"f5ba1ee8c6426d23efad159029b6fa293d289237","tid":532870,"uid":10881,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T09:02:22.000Z","msg":"睇下 email join 下校方活動啦<br />\n啲camp 都開始招爸媽oc , 準備去玩下啦<br />\n驚一個camp 唔夠chur 咪搞兩個lor <br />\n下年住hall 玩hall o lor <br />\njoin 多啲hall activities lor <br />\n